name: Get24
0:
”Alexa, Get Twenty-four.”
”One, two , three and four.”
”Show me four numbers.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: get twenty four
des:
A Complete reference for 24 game solving. Either give you a solution or let you know there is no solution. 
You can give me four numbers between 1 and 13, including 13. You need to add a word 'and' between the 3rd and 4th number. For example, "one, two , three and four."
Or, you can ask me for four numbers by saying "show me four numbers."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
